since Ron has now busted on me in public I may as well fess up -- I was
off the list from time to time lately 'cause I was playing in the series
-- Frustrated at my inability to break into the big leagues of poetry
book publishing, I've been moonlighting under a pseudonym for a ball team
-- The team at first seemed much more open to new talent than the world
of poetry, but now they've asked me to compose a "rap" for the team video
-- guess that was all they wanted me for all along --
